{"id":"api/core/testing","title":"@angular/core/testing","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core/testing\", \"name\": \"@angular/core/testing\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/core/testing/PACKAGE.md\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n<header class=\"api-header\">\n  <h1 id=\"angularcoretesting\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1fej7vpnovlqjm5a1u22afisz\">@angular/core/testing<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/testing#angularcoretesting\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n  <label class=\"api-type-label NaN\">entry-point</label>\n  \n  \n  \n</header>\n\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\"><p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dskt1vvqrfjvu9qk9xjo40zfl\">為測試 Angular 核心功能提供基礎設施</p>\n\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n\n<h2 id=\"entry-point-exports\">入口點的匯出<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/testing#entry-point-exports\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n  \n  \n  \n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \n  <section class=\"export-list\">\n    <h3 translation-result=\"on\" id=\"類別\">類別<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/testing#類別\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <h3 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"classes\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dtpuzegyjmcbul5yz5jn1ham3\">類別<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/testing#classes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <table class=\"is-full-width list-table\">\n      \n      <tbody><tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/testing/ComponentFixture\">ComponentFixture</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7r7i319l1xjhqv7iujwbcqioa\">用於除錯和測試元件的夾具。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/testing/DeferBlockFixture\">DeferBlockFixture</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ahcof2ciwm04opawddfr7v0bq\">為測試目的代表一個單獨的延遲區塊</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/testing/InjectSetupWrapper\">InjectSetupWrapper</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          \n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/testing/TestBed\">TestBed</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"64n0n1wgq7snbk7cbib0n5uxc\">設定和初始化用於單元測試的環境，並提供用於在單元測試中建立元件和服務的方法。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/testing/TestComponentRenderer\">TestComponentRenderer</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9sn8wx5l42mz4b8mtds89dsh9\">一個用於以與平台無關的方式插入根測試元件元素的抽象類別。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n    </tbody></table>\n  </section>\n  \n\n\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \n  <section class=\"export-list\">\n    <h3 translation-result=\"on\" id=\"函式\">函式<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/testing#函式\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <h3 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"functions\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dt2uvbdl3r7k4tmkiulzt8lb8\">函式<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/testing#functions\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <table class=\"is-full-width list-table\">\n      \n      <tbody><tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor deprecated-api-item\"><a href=\"api/core/testing/async\" class=\"deprecated-api-item\">async</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          <p><strong>已棄用:</strong> use <code><a href=\"api/core/testing/waitForAsync\" class=\"code-anchor\">waitForAsync</a>()</code>, (expected removal in v12)</p>\n\n          \n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/testing/discardPeriodicTasks\">discardPeriodicTasks</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4ooryhfqt0jjwbj9nmqjxbevn\">丟棄所有剩餘的定期任務。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/testing/fakeAsync\">fakeAsync</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"jvt3b4sisbiyrr93ugvw85mg\">包裝一個函式，以便在 <code><a href=\"api/core/testing/fakeAsync\" class=\"code-anchor\">fakeAsync</a></code> Zone 中執行：</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"inkmro6kxbrf8j1o8ip0wv7u\">透過呼叫 <code><a href=\"api/core/testing/flushMicrotasks\" class=\"code-anchor\">flushMicrotasks</a>()</code> 手動執行微任務，。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8cgpvaqb33d15mt9wdc0p1rg4\">計時器是同步的，用 <code><a href=\"api/core/testing/tick\" class=\"code-anchor\">tick</a>()</code> 模擬非同步時間的流逝。</li>\n</ul>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/testing/flush\">flush</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cwgkxhmt9jdp2fqpb886x4rut\">透過清空巨集任務佇列直到其為空，來為 fakeAsync Zone 中的計時器模擬非同步時間流逝。回傳的值是本應經過的毫秒數。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/testing/flushMicrotasks\">flushMicrotasks</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2c74nia3k6ftfvbul6a5ojk1c\">重新整理所有未完成的微任務。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/testing/getTestBed\">getTestBed</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"20rhw13xvirek25tycroieu4n\">回傳 <code><a href=\"api/core/testing/TestBed\" class=\"code-anchor\">TestBed</a></code> 類別的單例。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/testing/inject\">inject</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9088sqrsrcu2i3qfew6twxoi8\">允許在 <code>beforeEach()</code> 和 <code>it()</code> 中注入依賴項。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/testing/resetFakeAsyncZone\">resetFakeAsyncZone</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dq8qf6ga9l133c6xqepthh2gc\">清除共享的偽非同步 Zone 以進行測試。在全域 <code>beforeEach</code> 中呼叫。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/testing/tick\">tick</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bf3gff6ryygf60fcq5kkdshza\">為 fakeAsync Zone 中的計時器模擬非同步時間流逝。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/testing/waitForAsync\">waitForAsync</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"co37zyup43k1bj6do68hwz471\">把一個測試函式包裝進一個非同步測試 Zone。當該 Zone 中的所有非同步呼叫都已完成時，該測試將會自動完成。\n可用於包裝 <a href=\"api/core/testing/inject\"><code>inject</code></a> 呼叫。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/testing/withModule\">withModule</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          \n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n    </tbody></table>\n  </section>\n  \n\n\n  \n  \n  <section class=\"export-list\">\n    <h3 translation-result=\"on\" id=\"結構\">結構<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/testing#結構\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <h3 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"structures\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2pvj0r4hennzfp5hvt5swfw10\">結構<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/testing#structures\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <table class=\"is-full-width list-table\">\n      \n      <tbody><tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/testing/DeferBlockBehavior\">DeferBlockBehavior</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dqw1ivb157jpfhe5cgogpa2z6\">設定延遲區塊行為的選項</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/testing/DeferBlockState\">DeferBlockState</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bvz7uzoovx68y5opqwl03xhly\">描述此延遲區塊實例的當前狀態</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/testing/ModuleTeardownOptions\">ModuleTeardownOptions</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"64eumycvxns10ykzdqd4k2dnz\">在 <code><a href=\"api/core/testing/TestBed\" class=\"code-anchor\">TestBed</a></code> 中設定測試模組的拆卸行為。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/testing/TestBedStatic\">TestBedStatic</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"13tyo8iiw9b6k5atel12qt4kt\"><code><a href=\"api/core/testing/TestBed\" class=\"code-anchor\">TestBed</a></code> 實現的靜態方法。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/testing/TestEnvironmentOptions\">TestEnvironmentOptions</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          \n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/testing/TestModuleMetadata\">TestModuleMetadata</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          \n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n    </tbody></table>\n  </section>\n  \n\n\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \n  <section class=\"export-list\">\n    <h3 translation-result=\"on\" id=\"型別\">型別<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/testing#型別\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <h3 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"types\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"edj3fs52fiqyg9u6mdyxchcwv\">型別<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/testing#types\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <table class=\"is-full-width list-table\">\n      \n      <tbody><tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/testing/ComponentFixtureAutoDetect\">ComponentFixtureAutoDetect</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          \n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/testing/ComponentFixtureNoNgZone\">ComponentFixtureNoNgZone</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          \n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/testing/MetadataOverride\">MetadataOverride</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2id5zxz1t95ff65jplmnmrk8n\">用於修改元資料的型別</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n    </tbody></table>\n  </section>\n  \n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/testing/ComponentFixture\n - api/core/testing/ComponentFixtureAutoDetect\n - api/core/testing/ComponentFixtureNoNgZone\n - api/core/testing/DeferBlockBehavior\n - api/core/testing/DeferBlockFixture\n - api/core/testing/DeferBlockState\n - api/core/testing/InjectSetupWrapper\n - api/core/testing/MetadataOverride\n - api/core/testing/ModuleTeardownOptions\n - api/core/testing/TestBed\n - api/core/testing/TestBedStatic\n - api/core/testing/TestComponentRenderer\n - api/core/testing/TestEnvironmentOptions\n - api/core/testing/TestModuleMetadata\n - api/core/testing/async\n - api/core/testing/discardPeriodicTasks\n - api/core/testing/fakeAsync\n - api/core/testing/flush\n - api/core/testing/flushMicrotasks\n - api/core/testing/getTestBed\n - api/core/testing/inject\n - api/core/testing/resetFakeAsyncZone\n - api/core/testing/tick\n - api/core/testing/waitForAsync\n - a